 《OC》主创们透露了他们“后悔”的情节转折https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-oc-creators-reveal-plot-twist-they-regret-3484018?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-oc-creators-reveal-plot-twist-他们后悔Adam StarkeyWed, 16 Aug 2023 20:36:08 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3484018 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="该o.c。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “当时我们没有看到其他道路”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-o-c-creators-reveal-plot-twist-they-regret-3484018">《OC》的创作者透露了他们“遗憾”</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的情节转折。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="该o.c。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/theoc-cast-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>电视剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-oc"><em>《橘子郡》</em></a>的主创们表示，他们“遗憾”地杀死了米莎·巴顿饰演的深受粉丝喜爱的角色玛丽莎。</p><p>在该剧第三季结束时，玛丽莎遭遇车祸，死在男友瑞恩·阿特伍德（本·麦肯齐饰）的怀里。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-oc-one-tree-hill-nasvhille-friday-night-lights-gilmore-girls-soundtrack-2641769">从<em>OC</em>到<em>一树山</em>：naff 90 年代的节目配乐令人难以置信的酷</a></strong></li></ul><p>该剧主创乔什·施瓦茨（Josh Schwartz）和执行制片人斯蒂芬妮·萨维奇（Stephanie Savage）在该剧二十周年纪念日接受<a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2023/08/the-oc-20th-anniversary" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《名利场》</em></a>采访时，反思了杀死这个角色的决定。</p><p> “这是我们感到遗憾的事情，回顾过去，我们希望能够提出不同的解决方案，”施瓦茨说。 “当时我们没有看到其他道路，这就是我们走那条路的原因。 </p><figure id="attachment_2848813" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2848813" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2848813" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/HD853P.jpg" alt="该o.c" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/HD853P.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/HD853P-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/HD853P-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/HD853P-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/HD853P-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/HD853P-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2848813" class="wp-caption-text">蕾切尔·比尔森、亚当·布罗迪、米莎·巴顿和本杰明·麦肯齐在《橘子郡》第一季中。图片来源：华纳兄弟/埃弗里特收藏。</figcaption></figure><p> “但显然事后看来，我们还有很多其他方法可以让这个角色从剧中消失——并给米莎她需要和想要的休息时间——这仍然能让这个角色回归。”</p><p>施瓦茨表示，粉丝对她去世的负面反应“感觉不太好”，并补充道：“感觉观众没有按照我们一直想要和目标的方式得到服务或尊重。那时我们立刻就后悔了。”</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.eonline.com/news/1270301/mischa-barton-is-finally-ready-to-tell-the-real-story-behind-her-exit-from-the-o-c" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>E 采访时！</em></a> 2021年的<a href="https://www.eonline.com/news/1270301/mischa-barton-is-finally-ready-to-tell-the-real-story-behind-her-exit-from-the-o-c" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>消息</em></a>，巴顿<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/mischa-barton-claims-bullying-on-set-was-the-reason-she-left-the-o-c-2944313">声称片场“欺凌”是她想离开剧组的原因</a>。</p><p> “片场有人对我非常刻薄，”巴顿说。 “对于一个年轻、敏感的女孩来说，这并不是最理想的环境，她也被迫成为明星，不得不忍受。”</p><p>作为回应，巴顿的<em>《橘子郡》</em>联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-o-c-cast-respond-to-mischa-bartons-perplexing-claims-about-toxic-set-2954323">雷切尔·比尔森和梅琳达·克拉克表示，他们对她的说法感到“困惑”</a> 。</p><p> 2007 年， <em>《OC》</em>在四个赛季结束后结束，玛丽莎的去世导致收视率急剧下降。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-o-c-creators-reveal-plot-twist-they-regret-3484018">《OC》的创作者透露了他们“遗憾”</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的情节转折。</p> ;
